@startuml cafe-shell-init-sequence

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5

title CafeShell — DI context initialisation sequence

participant "new CafeShell(config)" as Shell
participant "CafeApplicationContext" as Ctx
participant "CafeCommandClassResolver" as ClassResolver
participant "CafeCommandMethodResolver" as MethodResolver
participant "CafeBeansFactory" as Factory

Shell -> Shell : beforeContextInit()\n  addBeanToContext(this)
Shell -> Ctx : initialize()
activate Ctx

Ctx -> Factory : resolve all scanned classes
activate Factory

loop for each @CafeCommand class
    Factory -> ClassResolver : resolve(classInfo, factory)
    activate ClassResolver

    ClassResolver -> ClassResolver : super.resolve()\n  → instantiate + inject fields
    ClassResolver -> ClassResolver : buildOption(@CafeCommand annotation)\n  → creates Apache CLI Option (or null for default commands)
    ClassResolver -> Factory : addToRepository(Option)
    ClassResolver -> ClassResolver : classInfo.getMethods()\n  .filter(@CafeCommandRun)\n  .findFirst() → CafeMethod
    ClassResolver -> Factory : addToRepository(CafeCommandOptionBinding\n  { instance, CafeMethod, Option })
    ClassResolver --> Factory : commandInstance
    deactivate ClassResolver
end

note over Factory: @CafeCommandRun methods are\nNOT invoked here — resolveMethod()\nis a no-op in CafeCommandClassResolver

Factory --> Ctx : all beans resolved
deactivate Factory
deactivate Ctx

Shell -> Shell : postContextInit()\n  createApacheOptions()\n  → getInstances(Option.class)\n  → options.addOption(each)

note over Shell: Context ready.\nOptions aggregate populated.\nAll CafeCommandOptionBindings\nstored in repository.

@enduml
